                        <summary>
                            <p>عين الحيات</p>
                            <p>A complete copy of the same poem [as W. 4], presented to Professor
                                Browne by Dr Rizá Tevfiq in August, 1909.</p>
                            <p>Ff. 90 of 22.2 x 15 c. and 22 ll. Clear Turkish naskh with
                                rubrications. Transcribed by Darwísh 'Abdu'l-Fattáh Yazíjí and
                                dated 9 Rajab 1217/5 November, 1802.</p>
                        </summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="W_5-item1">
