                            <title xml:lang="ar">عين الحيات</title>
                            <title xml:lang="en" type="desc">The Fountain of Life</title>
                            <note>A complete copy of the same poem as the defective copy at <ref
                                    target="../auto_update/W_4.xml">W. 4</ref>; the author's name
                                is given here in the rubric on f. 1. Transcribed by <persName
                                    role="scr" key="">Darwísh 'Abd al-Fattáh Yazíjí</persName>,
                                dated 9 Rajab 1217 (5 November 1802).</note>
